<D>__{fred, stop playing with dino and sit down. your breakfast's getting cold.}
<A>__{saying this, wilma puts a huge egg at fred's place. meanwhile, fred manages to get to his feet, holds out one arm to keep dino at bay. fred does a big "take," looking out the window }
<C>__{fred}
<P>__{(throwing open the door)}
<D>__{oooh, dino, look there's a nice big dino bone laying out on the front lawn !}
