<C>__{fred}
<P>__{(trying again)}
<D>__{ gosh, look at that adorable little female dino }
<A>__{"yi yi yi yi," dino is out the door like a rocket. fred cackles, slams it shut, then sits down at the table.}
<C>__{fred}
<D>__{ that animal's gonna kill me with kindness. do you know we're out of dino treats?}
<C>__{wilma}
<D>__{so is everybody else in bedrock. that kibble crisis is getting worse every day.}
<A>__{she puts two giant slices of bread into a toaster. two claw like devices hold the toast, pulling it out of sight.}
